tāmrapātraṃ tilaiḥ pūrṇaṃ sahiraṇyaṃ sadakṣiṇam  /<BR>
dadyādbrāhmaṇamukhyāya padadānaṃ tathaica  // GarP_2,4.130 //<BR>
yamoddeśetilāṃllauhaṃ tato dadyācca dakṣiṇām  /<BR>
