samuddharati tatkṣipraṃ nātra kāryā vicāraṇa nāgadaṃśānmṛto yastu viśeṣastantu me śṛṇu  // GarP_2,4.132 //<BR>
suvarṇabhāraniṣpannaṃ nāgaṃ kṛtvā tathaiva gām  /<BR>
viprāya dattvā vidhivatpiturānṛṇyamāpnuyāt  // GarP_2,4.133 //<BR>
evaṃ sarpabaliṃ dattvā sarpadoṣādvimucyate  /<BR>
paścātputtalakaṃ kāryaṃ sarvoṣadhisamanvitam  // GarP_2,4.134 //<BR>
palāśasya ca vṛntānāṃ vibhāgaṃ śṛṇu kāśyapa  /<BR>
kṛṣṇājinaṃ samāstīrya kuśaiśca puruṣākṛtim  // GarP_2,4.135 //<BR>
śatatrayeṇa ṣaṣṭyā ca vṛntaiḥ prokto 'sthisañcayaḥ  /<BR>
