pāradaṃ retasaḥ sthāne purīṣe pittalaṃ tathā  /<BR>
manaḥ śilā tathā gātre tilapakvantu sandhiṣu  // GarP_2,4.142 //<BR>
yavapiṣṭaṃ yathā māṃse madhu śoṇitameva ca  /<BR>
