vṛntākaṃ vṛṣaṇadvandve liṅge syādgṛñjanaṃ śubham  /<BR>
ghṛtaṃ nābhyāṃ pradeyaṃ syātkau pīne ca trapusmṛtam  // GarP_2,4.145 //<BR>
mauktikaṃ stanayormūrdhni kuṅkumeva vilepanam  /<BR>
