sarvamarmāṇi ṣaṣṭhena saptamena tu nāḍayaḥ  /<BR>
dantalomānyaṣṭamena vīryantu navamena ca  // GarP_2,5.36 //<BR>
daśamena tu pūrṇatvaṃ tṛptatā kṣudviparyayaḥ  /<BR>
