yayā viṣṇumayaṃ sarvamtmanyeva dadṛśivān  /<BR>
munaya ūcuḥ  /<BR>
śṛṇu vatsa pravakṣyā mo hitāya tava bālaka  // GarP_2,6.89 //<BR>
yena vai dhriyamāṇena ihāmutra sukhaṃ bhavet  /<BR>
