mātaraṃ bhaginīṃ bhāryāṃ snuṣāṃ duhitaraṃ tathā  /<BR>
adṛṣṭadoṣāṃ tyajati sa preto jāyatedhruvam  // GarP_2,22.14 //<BR>
bhrātṛdhrugbrahmahā goghnaḥ surāpo gurutalpagaḥ  /<BR>
