nityaṃ mṛtyurvaraṃ jantoḥ pretatvaṃ mā bhavetkvacit  // GarP_2,22.63 //<BR>
brāhmaṇa uvāca  /<BR>
upavāsaparo nityaṃ kṛcchracāndrāyaṇe rataḥ  /<BR>
